data.description: INVESTORS AND CASH BUYERS!!!! Looking for a private piece of property with room for a large family? Zoned AGR, so there is flexibility in use. Look no further!!  This nearly 1 1/2 acre property has room galore and needs work and  TLC to bring it back to its glory!  3 primary bedrooms and private baths and 1 full guest bath on 1st floor, 2 bedrooms and 1 shared bath on 2nd floor, finished attic space 410sf was used for 2 non-conforming bedrooms and not included in the 3307sf. Two detached garages. NEW ROOF 2023. HVAC units 3, 5, and 7 years old.   Property is being sold AS-IS.  Buyer to verify information.
